{"html":"<section id=\"frontispiece\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"full-page\" id=\"illustration-1\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"Three climbers stand on a mountain ridge and watch a cloud formation, in which an ellipsoid shape appears, crossed by three vertical lines.\" src=\"../images/illustration-1.png\"/>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Fog-bow seen from the Matterhorn on <time datetime=\"1865-07-14\">July 14, 1865</time>.<br/>\n\t\t\t\t“The Taugwalders thought that it had some connection with the accident.”</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t</section>"}